{"type":"message","id":"7ee1bbf6","parentId":"7ce8236b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:12:55.747Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1vlbiamzto5m_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session: 2026-04-09 14:12:03 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:coding-agent:feishu:direct:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\n- **Session ID**: a2015a07-00a3-48cf-b221-ca2dc6b9422c\n- **Source**: webchat\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nuser: A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 9th, 2026 - 10:10 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-09 14:10 UTC\nassistant: Hey, 张玲. Good to be back — today's session had a productive run with the omnicoder download, GLM-5.1 switch, and dashboard auto-sync set up. What are we working on tonight?\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 22:11 GMT+8] 你是什么模型\nassistant: 当前是 **MiniMax-M2.7**（`minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7`）。\n\n你昨天切到 GLM-5.1，但那是下个新 session 才生效。当前这个是配置切换之前开的，所以还是 MiniMax。在飞书重新发条消息，就是 GLM-5.1 了。\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 22:11 GMT+8] 怎么开一个new session\nassistant: 发送 `/new` 就可以开新 session，或者发 `/reset` 也可以。新 session 会用最新的配置（GLM-5.1）。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775743975741}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e169666","parentId":"7ee1bbf6","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:12:55.753Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1vlbiamzto5m_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-08 日志\n\n## 今日主要工作\n\n### 技能学习与整合\n1. **RD-Agent 评估** - 检查本地部署状态，发现 akshare 安装问题并修复\n2. **Superpowers 框架** - 从 obra/superpowers-skills 学习工程化工作流纪律\n3. **PUA 技能** - 通过 ClawHub 安装 tanweai/pua 技能包\n4. **Everything Claude Code** - 学习 affaan-m/everything-claude-code 框架\n5. **三大框架整合** - 更新 superpowers-integration/SKILL.md\n\n### 模型切换\n- 从 MiniMax-M2.5 切换到 MiniMax-M2.7\n\n### 股市数据\n- 4月8日 A股大涨：上证+2.7%，深证+4.79%，创业板+5.91%\n- 原因：中东局势缓和，油价下跌，全球股市反弹\n\n## 待处理\n- 量化系统全面自检提示词 - 用户发送了一个完整的自检框架，需要协助执行\n- RD-Agent 评估 - 用户问是否值得更新，尚未完成"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775743975748}}
