{"type":"message","id":"b79c4f6e","parentId":"d389b8e1","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:35:43.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to fix the issues one by one. Let me look at the high priority issues first and create a plan for fixing them.\n\nHigh priority issues:\n1. 系统单点故障风险 - 引入备份机制或云服务器\n2. 回测-实盘偏差大 - 增加样本外验证、加入滑点成本\n3. 极端行情应对缺失 - 制定涨跌停应急流程\n\nBut wait - I don't know what their actual trading system looks like. I need to ask what system they're using (什么量化交易系统？掘金？聚宽？自研？)，以及当前的一些具体情况，才能针对性地帮助修复。\n\nLet me ask for more context about their actual system.\n","thinkingSignature":"4b6d2efca6328efcd10d77f16998a6d3c97529b272e42bf6181a28ae1616495c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n逐一修复可以，但需要先了解你的实际情况：\n\n**请告诉我：**\n1. 你目前用什么交易系统？（掘金/聚宽/同花顺/自研Python/其他）\n2. 当前服务器/电脑的部署情况？（本地/云/一台还是多台）\n3. 主要做哪个周期的策略？（T+1/日内/高频）\n\n这样我才能帮你针对性地修复，而不是给通用方案。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":439,"output":230,"cacheRead":33088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33757,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775745330488,"responseId":"0626ec33c1113718eb940dcc798d8246"}}
