{"type":"message","id":"2dc7f459","parentId":"c9997f1f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:42:57.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've generated a comprehensive fix plan for the user's quantitative system based on Tonghuashun + multiple computers + medium-low frequency strategy. Now let me summarize it for them in Chinese.\n","thinkingSignature":"914ac95d91df45032c7d053bbbb3a5f664263d84c06c9c1ea37f21db0aae246a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已生成修复方案，保存在 `memory/量化系统修复方案-2026-04-09.md`\n\n针对同花顺+多电脑+中低频的核心修复：\n\n| 优先级 | 修复项 | 方案 |\n|--------|--------|------|\n| 🔴 高 | 极端行情应急 | 14:45自动检查，跌7%强平 |\n| 🔴 高 | 仓位控制 | 单票≤10%，单行业≤20% |\n| 🔴 高 | 主备切换 | 备机同步，异常自动切换 |\n| ⚠️ 中 | 监控告警 | 异常微信/钉钉通知 |\n| ⚠️ 中 | 回测偏差修正 | 加滑点、剔除极端行情 |\n| ⚠️ 中 | 文档管理 | 飞书/Notion规范化 |\n\n**执行顺序建议**：先做极端行情应急 + 仓位控制（保护本金），再做主备切换 + 监控告警，最后回测修正 + 文档体系。\n\n需要我帮你：\n1. **写具体脚本**（主备切换/告警/数据校验）？\n2. **搭建飞书文档库**（创建结构）？\n\n你先说最急的，我直接开干。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1397,"output":290,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35479,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775745761721,"responseId":"0626ede3dd053f90395eee2e0d501e3b"}}
