{"type":"message","id":"15be961f","parentId":"e43b5dbd","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:52:39.584Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I created 3 scripts for the user. Let me summarize what was created.\n","thinkingSignature":"f303802055cdc09ca7a416356f0f7e71a72c693ec811ca164bda6684ee0ee803"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已创建 3 个脚本，保存在 `scripts/` 目录：\n\n| 脚本 | 功能 | 位置 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `monitor_backup.py` | 主备切换监控 | 监控主力机状态，异常自动切换到备机 |\n| `trade_monitor.py` | 交易异常告警 | 监控滑点、持仓亏损、当日盈亏，触发告警 |\n| `data_validator.py` | 数据校验 | 检测价格/成交量异常、OHLC逻辑错误、缺失值 |\n\n**使用方式**：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 主备监控（后台运行）\npython scripts/monitor_backup.py\n\n# 2. 交易监控（后台运行）\npython scripts/trade_monitor.py\n\n# 3. 数据校验（手动）\npython scripts/data_validator.py 你的数据.csv\n```\n\n**需要配置**：\n- `WEBHOOK_URL` - 填入你的钉钉/飞书Webhook才能收到告警\n- `PRIMARY_HOST` - 改成你主力机的实际IP地址\n- 根据你的同花顺API实际情况调整API调用部分\n\n需要我帮你调整某个脚本的具体配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2851,"output":257,"cacheRead":35904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39012,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775746348179,"responseId":"0626f02c8f065b1da10d7c17fd574810"}}
